      "Step 3: Select the tool. The instrument designed to measure Volts is the Voltmeter."
    ],
    "questionText": "You are called to a kitchen where a socket has stopped working. You need to measure the electrical pressure at the terminals to see if 230V is present. Which specific instrument should you use?",
