      "This quantity is measured in Ohms.",
      "Using the correct instrument ensures you are measuring the physical property of the component, not the live circuit flow."
    ],
    "questionText": "You are testing an immersion heater element that has failed. You need to measure the element's opposition to current flow to check for a break in the internal wire. Which specific instrument must you select for this task?",
